    Enum Constant and Description
    com.license4j.ModificationStatus.MODIFICATION_KEY_INVALID
    MODIFICATION_KEY_INVALID is never returned as of release 4.4.0 due to new special key feature. Since any string can be defined as a special modification key, it is not validated; directly send to server for validation and modification.
